Underlining the text in HTML

<style>
    .underline-text {
      font-family: Arial;
      background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.46) ;
      color: white;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 15px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      padding-right: 15px;
    }

    .span-example:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .your-text {
        cursor:pointer;
    }

    .your-text:hover {
     text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>

<p class ="underline-text">
    Super cool unicode text magic. Underline <span class = "your-text">your text</span> on Facebook, Twitter, and everywhere else.
</p>
